  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_180_000226",
    "sentence": "或尋為篡奪，或僅傳子孫，咸非令終，蓋其宜也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_180_000227",
    "sentence": "贊曰：蠍石之野，氣勁人豪。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_180_000228",
    "sentence": "二百餘載，自相尊高。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_180_000229",
    "sentence": "載義、仲武，亦多忠勞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
